{"tid":2111462,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［突發 (Poly)］狗聽朝（17日）用搜查令搜Poly VA core","createTime":"2020-07-16T14:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T04:28:18.000Z","uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4754b1a8adb60414e22d903269a70d086e160040","tid":2111462,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T14:13:30.000Z","msg":"理工大學去年 11 月發生嚴重的警民衝突，其中在 11 月 17 日，一名傳媒聯絡隊成員小腿中箭受傷，送院治療。事隔八個月，香港理工大學學生會今日晚上（16日）收到警方通知，指警方將會連同搜查令在翌日早上 8 時搜查該校邵逸夫樓 VA Core ，亦即學生會大樓。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%98%8E%E6%90%9C%E6%9F%A5%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83%E5%A4%A7%E6%A8%93-%E6%88%96%E8%88%87%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E4%B8%AD%E7%AE%AD%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259C%2583-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%2590%259C%25E6%259F%25A5%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A8%2593-%25E6%2588%2596%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25AE%25AD%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2597%259C%2F&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFaRSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=bf210409\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259C%2583-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%2590%259C%25E6%259F%25A5%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A8%2593-%25E6%2588%2596%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25AE%25AD%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2597%259C%2F&h=fc152611\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E7%90%86%E